1 (c) This section does not affect unfair trade practices otherwise
2 actionable at common law or under other statutes of this state.
3 Sec. 18. This act becomes operative on January 1, 2027.
4 Sec. 19. Original section 87-302, Revised Statutes Supplement,
5 2025, is repealed.
